 Vazquez - Professional Profile\",\"description\":\"Professional profile of Isaac Vazquez - Technical Product Manager and UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate with expertise in product strategy, quality engineering, analytics, and fintech-style product work.\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-04-03T00:31:16.132Z\",\"mainEntity\":{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"@id\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com#person\",\"name\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"alternateName\":\"Isaac Vazquez\",\"description\":\"Product manager with a technical background building products across SaaS, civic technology, and fintech-style platforms. Expertise in product strategy, user research, quality assurance, and data-driven decision making.\",\"url\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com\",\"image\":\"https://isaacavazquez.com/opengraph-image\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://linkedin.com/in/isaac-vazquez\",\"https://github.com/IsaacAVazquez\",\"https://twitter.com/isaacvazquez\"],\"jobTitle\":\"Technical Product Manager & UC Berkeley Haas MBA Candidate\",\"email\":\"IsaacVazquez@berkeley.edu\",\"hasCredential\":[{\"@type\":\"EducationalOccupationalCredential\",\"name\":\"Product Management\",\"competencyRequired\":\"Advanced\",\"credentialCategory\":\"Skill\",\"validFor\":\"P3Y\"},{\"@type\":\"EducationalOccupationalCredential\",\"name\":\"Quality Assurance\",\"competencyRequired\":\"Expert\",\"credentialCategory\":\"Skill\",\"validFor\":\"P6Y\"},{\"@type\":\"EducationalOccupationalCredential\",\"name\":\"Data Analysis\",\"competencyRequired\":\"Advanced\",\"credentialCategory\":\"Skill\",\"validFor\":\"P6Y\"},{\"@type\":\"EducationalOccupationalCredential\",\"name\":\"Fintech Product Development\",\"competencyRequired\":\"Intermediate\",\"credentialCategory\":\"Skill\",\"validFor\":\"P1Y\"}],\"alumniOf\":[{\"@type\":\"CollegeOrUniversity\",\"name\":\"UC Berkeley Haas School of Business\",\"description\":\"MBA Candidate (Class of 2027)\",\"startDate\":\"2025-08\",\"endDate\":\"2027-05\"},{\"@type\":\"CollegeOrUniversity\",\"name\":\"Florida State University\",\"description\":\"Bachelor of Arts - Political Science and International Affairs\",\"endDate\":\"2018\"}]}}</script><section class=\"page-section min-h-screen bg-[var(--surface-primary)]\"><div class=\"page-shell space-y-10\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"space-y-4 mx-auto text-center items-center max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"flex justify-center\"><span class=\"section-kicker\">About</span></div><h1 class=\"font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.02]\">A product manager with roots in QA, analytics, and execution.</h1><p class=\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose section-subtitle mb-0 mx-auto\">My background combines product strategy with hands-on experience in quality, systems thinking, and cross-functional delivery.</p></div></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex justify-center\"><div role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"About sections\" class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-secondary)] p-2.5 shadow-sm\"><button id=\"overview-tab\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"overview-panel\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors bg-[var(--text-primary)] text-[var(--text-inverse)] shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"tabler-icon tabler-icon-user h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 7a4 4 0 1 0 8 0a4 4 0 0 0 -8 0\"></path><path d=\"M6 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4 -4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2\"></path></svg><span>Overview</span></button><button id=\"journey-tab\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"journey-panel\" tabindex=\"-1\" class=\"flex min-h-[48px] items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors text-[var(--text-secondary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-primary)] hover:text-[var(--text-primary)]\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"tabler-icon tabler-icon-timeline h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 16l6 -7l5 5l5 -6\"></path><path d=\"M14 14a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0\"></path><path d=\"M9 9a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0\"></path><path d=\"M3 16a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0\"></path><path d=\"M19 8a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0\"></path></svg><span>Journey</span></button></div></div><div id=\"overview-panel\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"overview-tab\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-10 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 shadow-sm\" role=\"article\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><h2 class=\"sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6 text-2xl lg:text-3xl\">Overview</h2><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\">I&#x27;m a technical product manager with a background in QA and analytics. At Civitech I work across quality and product for platforms that serve 60M+ users, helping teams turn complex system and user signals into practical decisions.</p><div><p class=\"mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-lg\">What I bring:</p><ul class=\"ml-6 list-disc space-y-3 text-base text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\"><li><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Product &amp; Strategy:</strong> <!-- -->Define the problem clearly, balance user and business needs, and keep teams aligned around the right outcome.</li><li><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Technical:</strong> <!-- -->Work comfortably with automation, SQL, and APIs so product decisions stay connected to how the system actually works.</li><li><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Analytics:</strong> <!-- -->Use data to understand what&#x27;s working, test assumptions, and make measurement useful to the team doing the work.</li><li><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Fintech Curiosity:</strong> <!-- -->Build investment research and analytics projects to stay close to how product design and decision support come together.</li><li><strong class=\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Leadership:</strong> <!-- -->Support launches, mentor teammates, and help create the clarity teams need to ship well.</li></ul></div><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\">Before Civitech I led client services at Open Progress, running 80+ digital programs, building data pipelines, and using audience analytics to make campaigns resonate with the people on the other end.</p><p class=\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\">I&#x27;m earning my MBA at UC Berkeley Haas to deepen the strategy side of the work while continuing to build products that help people make better decisions.</p><p class=\"text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-lg\">I&#x27;m especially interested in products that sit at the intersection of analytics, trust, and clear user decision-making.</p></div></div></div></div><div id=\"journey-panel\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"journey-tab\" hidden=\"\"></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div><footer role=\"contentinfo\" aria-label=\"Site footer\" data-footer-variant=\"full\" class=\"relative z-20 border-t border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-primary)]\"><div class=\"page-shell py-12 md:py-16\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 md:p-10 section-panel\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"max-w-2xl text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Thanks for taking a look.</h2><p class=\"max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)]\">If a project stands out, I&#x27;d be happy to share more about the work or my background.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row\"><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors bg-[var(--text-primary)] text-[var(--text-inverse)] hover:bg-[var(--neutral-800)]\" href=\"/portfolio\">View projects<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M5 12l14 0\"></path><path d=\"M13 18l6 -6\"></path><path d=\"M13 6l6 6\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex min-h-[48px] items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl border px-6 py-3 font-medium transition-colors border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-primary)] text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--surface-secondary)]\" href=\"/contact\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"h-4 w-4\"><path d=\"M3 7a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-10z\"></path><path d=\"M3 7l9 6l9 -6\"></path></svg>Get in touch</a></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-5 border-t pt-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between mt-8 border-[var(--border-primary)]\"><div class=\"space-y-1 text-sm text-[var(--text-tertiary)]\"><p class=\"font-medium text-[var(--text-primary)]\">Isaac Vazquez</p><p>Product management, projects, and analytics-focused work.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:items-end\"><n