ch I work across quality and product for platforms that serve 60M+ users, helping teams turn complex system and user signals into practical decisions.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"What I bring:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"ml-6 list-disc space-y-3 text-base text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Product & Strategy:\"}],\" \",\"Define the problem clearly, balance user and business needs, and keep teams aligned around the right outcome.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Technical:\"}],\" \",\"Work comfortably with automation, SQL, and APIs so product decisions stay connected to how the system actually works.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Analytics:\"}],\" \",\"Use data to understand what's working, test assumptions, and make measurement useful to the team doing the work.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Fintech Curiosity:\"}],\" \",\"Build investment research and analytics projects to stay close to how product design and decision support come together.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Leadership:\"}],\" \",\"Support launches, mentor teammates, and help create the clarity teams need to ship well.\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Before Civitech I led client services at Open Progress, running 80+ digital programs, building data pipelines, and using au