t text-[var(--text-primary)] text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.02]\",\"children\":\"A product manager with roots in QA, analytics, and execution.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm lg:text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-secondary)] leading-relaxed max-inline-size-prose section-subtitle mb-0 mx-auto\",\"children\":\"My background combines product strategy with hands-on experience in quality, systems thinking, and cross-functional delivery.\"}],null]}]}],\"$L3\"]}]}]],null,\"$L4\"]}],\"loading\":null,\"isPartial\":false}\n3:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L5\",null,{\"overviewContent\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-10 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 shadow-sm\",\"role\":\"article\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[var(--text-primary)] mb-6 text-2xl lg:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"Overview\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"I'm a technical product manager with a background in QA and analytics. At Civitech I work across quality and product for platforms that serve 60M+ users, helping teams turn complex system and user signals into practical decisions.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-3 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"What I bring:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"ml-6 list-disc space-y-3 text-base text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Product & Strategy:\"}],\" \",\"Define the problem clearly, balance user and business needs, and keep teams aligned around the right outcome.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Technical:\"}],\" \",\"Work comfortably with automation, SQL, and APIs so product decisions stay connected to how the system actually works.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Analytics:\"}],\" \",\"Use data to understand what's working, test assumptions, and make measurement useful to the team doing the work.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Fintech Curiosity:\"}],\" \",\"Build investment research and analytics projects to stay close to how product design and decision support come together.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-[var(--text-primary)]\",\"children\":\"Leadership:\"}],\" \",\"Support launches, mentor teammates, and help create the clarity teams need to ship well.\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"Before Civitech I led client services at Open Progress, running 80+ digital programs, building data pipelines, and using audience analytics to make campaigns resonate with the people on the other end.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"I'm earning my MBA at UC Berkeley Haas to deepen the strategy side of the work while continuing to build products that help people make better decisions.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-base font-medium leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-primary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"I'm especially interested in products that sit at the intersection of analytics, trust, and clear user decision-making.\"}]]}]}]}],\"journeyContent\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-5xl\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-xl bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] border border-[var(--border-primary)] transition-all duration-200 ease-out hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-[var(--border-accent)] cursor-pointer p-10 sm:p-12 lg:p-16\",\"role\":\"article\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-2xl text-[var(--color-primary)] lg:text-3xl\",\"children\":\"Career Journey\"}],\"$L6\"]}],\"$L7\"]}]}]}]}]}]\n4:[\"$\",\"$L8\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$9\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@a\"}]}]\n6:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-[var(--text-secondary)] md:text-lg\",\"children\":\"From Political Science graduate to QA engineer, and now an MBA candidate at UC Berkeley, my career has been a journey of continuous learning and impact. Here's a snapshot of my professional timeline.\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"2018-Bachelor of Arts Graduate\",{\"className\":\"group relative flex items-start gap-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative flex flex-col items-center\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"relative z-10 mb-4 h-16 w-16 rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--border-primary)] bg-[var(--surface-elevated)] p-2\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-full w-full items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-[var(--surface-elevated)]\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$Lb\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/logos/fsu-logo.png\",\"alt\":\"Florida State University logo\",\"width\":48,\"height\":48,\"className\":\"object-contain\"